                    ---------------------
                 *  POWER Procedures 2.00  *
                    ---------------------


    A complete set of more than 50 procedures to give an intuition look
    to your programs.

    Fully functional version with NO MORE limitation !

    This procedures are SHAREWARE : 100 FF or US $20 only.

    Include a complete executable demonstration !

    The procedures require AMOS or AMOS Pro or Easy AMOS langage.


    ---------------------
    New in version 2.00 :
    ---------------------

    - Removed all shareware protection checkings : Speed increase :-)
    - Unlocked all procedures :->
    - Reduced the size of many procedures using auto-handling mode
    - Used global variables PW_XMIN, PW_XMAX, PW_YMIN, PW_YMAX
      for easier zones definition and changed many return parameters
    - Corrected faults in english doc (FONT parameter missing)
    - Updated documentation (more links, ...)

    - Modified  PW_BUTTON1,2 : Added auto-handling (mouse and keyboard)
    - Modified  PW_COLOR, PW_RADIO, PW_WINDOW : Added auto-handling (mouse)
    - Modified  PW_WINDOW : Deleted 2 parameters
    - Modified  PW_TEXT : Added FONT parameter
    - Modified  PW_INPUT1,2,3,4 : Added cursor auto-pointing
    - Modified  PW_REQUEST1,2,3,4,5,6 : Renamed parameter PW_MZ to PW_SELECTED
    - Modified  PW_PALETTE, PW_COLORS : Added [Return] and [Esc] support
    - Modified  PW_PALETTE, PW_REQUESTER : Renamed parameter PW_MZ to PW_SELECTED
    - Corrected PW_REQUESTER : Removed few bugs


